The Symbiotic Evolution: Humans and AI crafting the future together.

The AI Coding Revolution

AI is actively reshaping software development, impacting how code is written, tested, and deployed. This is viewed as a symbiotic evolution, augmenting human ingenuity rather than replacing it.

Historically, AI assistance dates back to the 1960s (PLATO), evolving from rudimentary completion to the massive leap brought by LLMs in 2022.

Timeline of Intelligence
1960s

PLATO: The first seeds of AI in education.

1990s

Rudimentary code completion tools appear.

2022

ChatGPT triggers the Generative AI era.
